  <brief_title>A Study of Mifepristone vs. Placebo in the Treatment of Patients With Major Depression With Psychotic Features</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled Study of the Efficacy and Safety of Mifepristone vs. Placebo in the Treatment of Psychotic Symptoms in Patients With Major Depressive Disorder With Psychotic Features</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
